Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.50,0:02:44.95,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}一個人天花板 盯著的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.92,0:02:49.16,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}包羅萬象什麼的 無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.16,0:02:51.33,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}腦袋裡面載入
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.33,0:02:53.46,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}是不是不可能的嘛
Comment: 0,0:02:53.46,0:02:55.30,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}Go ask my instincts
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.51,0:03:16.64,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}一直響著的沉默的警鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.64,0:03:18.86,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}那又是誰的規矩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.86,0:03:21.46,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}不要迷茫跳進去跳進去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.46,0:03:23.82,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}站起來 破壞掉這無理的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.82,0:03:25.41,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}如果解不開這沉默
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.41,0:03:27.83,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}就大喊露鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.83,0:03:30.16,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}直到終幕我都要說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.16,0:03:33.03,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}Gear up! 這不是玩笑
